svg.title: Deck of Cards
svg.desc:
Deck of Cards
Based on the openclipart White Deck of individual cards by nicubunu for example https://openclipart.org/detail/23117/white-deck-ace-of-clubs
Click on any card to display the card Click on the card to display the deck again
Cards are symbols for reuse in card games
Jay Nick STEAMcoded.org
